*Minuta* je proletela, kao da je bila sekunda. (The minute flew by, as if it was a second.)

*Minut* je dovoljan da bi se završili zadaci. (A minute is enough to finish the tasks.)

Danas je trajalo nekoliko *minuta* pre nego što je procenila situaciju. (Today it took several minutes before she assessed the situation.)

On je potrošio svoje vreme u *minutima*. (He spent his time in minutes.)

Žena je živela u neznanju više od *minut*. (The woman lived in ignorance more than a minute.)